    <h1>What I Learned and Enjoyed in Programming</h1>
    <p>
        During my journey in learning programming, I greatly enjoyed exploring fundamental concepts such as **Data Structures** and algorithms. Understanding how to organize data and the efficiency of problem-solving was incredibly fascinating. I also enjoyed applying **Python** to write simple code and create small programs, especially in the field of data analysis, where I found its flexibility and readability very appealing. Learning to build basic user interfaces using **HTML and CSS** was also enjoyable, as it allowed me to see the visual results of my work instantly.
